parameters: Noble Cresso: Could you please leave?

Clea: I've looked at the request form. I will definitely
retrieve the ring.

Noble Cresso: Have you seen the sign outside? It seems that
this place used to be a blacksmith shop until a few years
ago.

Noble Cresso: If you say you like this village, young noble
Lud will make preparations for you.

Noble Cresso: You took care of my son and daughter-in-law,
didn't you?

Clea: I'm sorry. If only I had arrived at the scene a little
earlier...!

Noble Cresso: You don't have to apologize. Lud has been
asking about you.

Noble Cresso: I heard that you belong to the Adventurer's
Guild.
Clea: Why... didn't you ask for a request?

Noble Cresso: I heard they were young women, but I just
didn't feel like contacting the guild.

Noble Cresso: This must also be the guidance of the divine
god Sol. I have heard that the ring ended up in the slums of
the defeated soldiers.
Clea: Understood, I will definitely retrieve it.
Noble Cresso: Ah, I'm counting on you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Mycos Region / Slums of the
Defeated Soldiers\c[0]

Noble Cresso: Please don't push yourself. There's no need to
compare life and a ring.
クエスト:再開クリア済

Clea: Here is the promised ring. It's a memento ring, are
you sure it's the right one?

Noble Clea: Indeed, it is the one I gave to my son. Thank
you for retrieving his memento.

Noble Clea: It seems like you have something to say to me.
If you don't mind, would you let me hear it?

Clea: My parents were killed by a dragon, and I have
dedicated everything to seek revenge.

Noble Clea: Have you gained anything from seeking revenge?
In many cases, all that remains is an indescribable
emptiness.

Clea: Indeed, that may be true. However, I believe it was
necessary to take a new step forward.

Clea: To live while forgetting everything... that means
forgetting about the important people too.

Clea: Please take a look at this memento ring and remember
the memories of your loved ones.

Noble Clea: I apologize for the reward of the promise, but
could you leave me alone for a moment?

Noble Clea: Take a look at this memento ring... So, what is
it that you all want from me?

Clea: Here is the promised ring. It's a memento ring, are
you sure it's the right one?

Noble Clea: Indeed, it is the one I gave to my son. Thank
you for retrieving his memento.
Clea: Please give me the next request.

Noble Clea: What are you talking about? The request to you
should have already been completed.
Clea: It's not over. We should avenge my sons!
Clea: If we don't... if we don't!
Noble Clea: Can't you affirm yourself?

Noble Clea: I should have told you that I heard it from
Lloyd-kun. I want to hear about your background and the
reason why you fight.

Clea: Aren't you frustrated... having someone precious taken
away from you unjustly...

Clea: Is the person who took them away still alive?! Or am I
supposed to live here safely?!
Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan, you're going too far.

Clea: Please look at this keepsake ring that only a living
person can do something with... and think about it...!

Clea: I'm waiting for your request. I will definitely defeat
the Aspida Alliance.

Noble Clea: I don't mind. I have also heard about her
parents.

Noble Clea: I apologize for the reward of the promise, but
could you leave me alone?

Noble Clea: Look at this keepsake ring... So, what do you
all want from me?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Noble Cresso: I apologize for asking you to come.
Clea: I apologize for that time...

Noble Cresso: I cannot affirm revenge, as it would deny the
kindness and the living son and daughter-in-law.

Clea: Could you please tell me the true meaning behind this
request?

Noble Cresso: I have been gazing at the ring you brought
back.

Noble Cresso: The day my son was born, the day my wife died,
the day my son brought back an important woman...

Noble Cresso: This ring has been by my side, watching over
the important moments of my life.

Noble Cresso: We must not create humans like me who thought
it was no longer permissible to steal.

Clea: Understood. I will destroy the Aspida Alliance so that
such tragedy never happens again.

Noble Cresso: I want to request something from you, with the
prayer that someone's kindness will be protected.

Noble Cresso: Please head towards the abandoned castle where
they have made their stronghold.

Noble Cresso: Ah, take care. I sincerely pray for your
safety.
Noble Cresso: Is this alright...? Yes, my son?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Valt Region / Abandoned Castle
of the Aspida Alliance\c[0]

Noble Cresso: Please make sure not to push yourself too
hard.

Noble Cresso: It seems that you have annihilated the Aspida
Alliance. Although it appears that there are still remnants
lingering in the abandoned city.
Noble Cresso: A friend came and investigated your movements.

Clea: I was once taught by someone I respected not to be
consumed by emotions.

Clea: I just... feel like I ended up fighting not as a hired
hand, but as an individual when facing the enemy.
Clea: I am still... truly inexperienced.

Noble Cresso: My son and his wife... they had a hobby of
gardening and would raise plants together while making a
fuss.

Noble Cresso: When asked what was enjoyable, they said it
was the fact that no two plants grew the same.

Noble Cresso: As adventurers, I suppose you all grow
differently as individuals.

Noble Cresso: You should walk your own path. Thanks to you,
I feel like I can take a new step forward.
Clea: Yes, thank you very much.

Noble Cresso: This is the promised reward... Also, if
possible, would you mind taking this ring as well?
Clea: I can't accept something so important!

Noble Cresso: Because it's important, I believe my son and
his wife would be happy if you lend a helping hand to
someone in need.
Clea: ...I understand, I will treasure it.

Noble Cresso: Thank you for completing the request. May your
days of adventure be filled with happiness.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Cresso: The villagers kindly taught me how to start
gardening.
Noble Cresso: Every day is a continuous discovery.

Noble Cresso: It may not look great, but it's my first
creation.

Noble Cresso: I would like you to make use of your
adventures if you'd like.
Noble Cresso: I pray for the safety of your journey.
